{"lastModified":1774278581830,"uri":"c::22520698802::vessel::93200c60-6061-11ef-a458-cf0446e40ec2","yachtType":["Motor","Power Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Indian Ocean/Andaman Ocean. Specifically: West Sumatra—Mentawai Islands, Tello Islands, Nias Island. North Sumatra/Ache, Phuket.\n\n\nAsk anybody who knows about Surf Charters in Mentawaiis and you'll hear MV Addiction is among the very top vessels to cruise in the area. Over 15 years at sea and always one of the best service and most confortable boat you can find on the market.\n\nAnother important feature is speed. Speed means less time crossing, checking waves, stressing about missing sessions and more time surfing, exploring, enjoying. MV Addiction is among the fastest and stable boat in Mentawaiis. A luxury you can only realise after having a trip on such boat but which makes the whole difference with classic charters.\n\nMV Addiction standard trip is for 10 people only. We can take an extra 2 people (max of 12) for additional cost.\n\nOperating Area:  Mentawaii Islands and North or South Sumatra, Tello Islands. •\tAdditional fuel surcharge for northern Sumatra extended routes","blueprint":{"name":"ADDICTION","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::93200c60-6061-11ef-a458-cf0446e40ec2::assets::b95b61d0-6062-11ef-a7df-05b5cdcaa38f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::93200c60-6061-11ef-a458-cf0446e40ec2::assets::c3ef34f0-6062-11ef-a7df-05b5cdcaa38f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::93200c60-6061-11ef-a458-cf0446e40ec2::assets::c3ed8740-6062-11ef-a7df-05b5cdcaa38f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::93200c60-6061-11ef-a458-cf0446e40ec2::assets::c3f109b0-6062-11ef-a7df-05b5cdcaa38f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::93200c60-6061-11ef-a458-cf0446e40ec2::assets::c3f01f50-6062-11ef-a7df-05b5cdcaa38f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::93200c60-6061-11ef-a458-cf0446e40ec2::assets::c3eebfc0-6062-11ef-a7df-05b5cdcaa38f/{imageVariant}